Package: pba
Version: 0.2-1
Date: 2011-03-25
Title: Probabilistic Bias Analysis
Author@R: person("Jeremy", "Hetzel", "Thoms",
				 email = "jthetzel@gmail.com")
Author: Jeremy T. Hetzel <jthetzel@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Jeremy T. Hetzel <jthetzel@gmail.com>
Depends: R (>= 2.12.0), plyr, ggplot2, QRMlib, reshape, roxygen
Description: The pba package performs probabilistic bias analyses, with methods are adapted from Lash TL, Fox MP, and Fink AK's Applying Quantitative Bias Analysis to Epidemiological Data (2010). Currently, only methods for adjustment of misclassification bias are included.
License: GPL-3
URL: http://pba.r-forge.r-project.org/
BugReports: https://r-forge.r-project.org/tracker/?func=add&group_id=988&atid=3913		 
LazyLoad: yes
LazyData: yes				 